casebody.head_matter:
Dana Leon BROOKS, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES.
No. 15-8015.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 28, 2016.
On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals of Ninth Circuit. Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for Ninth Circuit for further consideration in light of Mathis v. United States, 579 U.S. ----, 136 S.Ct. 2243, --- L.Ed.2d ---- (2016).
